            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d82102-Hd1e108">Rubrica 16</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d82102-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De reuerentia et honorificatione</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d82102-d1e114">
               <lb ed="#V" n="52"/>
      ¶ De reuerentia et honorificatio
      <lb ed="#V" n="53"/>ne. Rubrica. 16 
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d82102-d1e121">
               <lb ed="#V" n="54"/>
       <ref>IN leuitico. ca. 19.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="55"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d82102-Qd1e125">Coram causa
        <lb ed="#V" n="56"/>non capite consurge et honora perso
        <lb ed="#V" n="57"/>nam senis.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d82102-d1e135">
               <lb ed="#V" n="58"/>
          <ref>¶ Cronica de nugis philosophorum. c. 4 scilice
        <lb ed="#V" n="59"/>de chilone.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d82102-Qd1e139">Chilo lacedemonius qui fuit vnus
        <lb ed="#V" n="60"/>de septem sapientibus iubebat senium honorare.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d82102-d1e148">
               <lb ed="#V" n="61"/>
       <ref>¶ Aristotelis retho. lib. i. c. 5.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d82102-Qd1e152">Irreuerentia est
        <lb ed="#V" n="62"/>paruipensio et despectus. quos enim mul
        <lb ed="#V" n="63" break="no"/>tum despicimus non reueremur.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d82102-d1e160"> 
       <ref>/ Li. 2 c.
        <lb ed="#V" n="64"/>17.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d82102-Qd1e162">Reuerentiores facit dignitas. Reueren
        <lb ed="#V" n="65"/>tia est mollis et decens grauitas.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d82102-d1e170"> 
          <ref>/ Lib. 3. et
        <lb ed="#V" n="66"/>fi. c. 16.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d82102-Qd1e172">Oportet bonos honorari.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d82102-d1e178"> 
          <ref>/ Idem
        <lb ed="#V" n="67"/>pollyticorum: li. c. 7.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d82102-Qd1e180">Rationabiliter prepa
        <lb ed="#V" n="68" break="no"/>rantur honori nobiles et diuites.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d82102-d1e188">
               <lb ed="#V" n="69"/>
         <ref>¶ Iesus filius sirach: in ecclesiast. c. 11.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d82102-Qd1e192">In
        <lb ed="#V" n="70"/>medio seniorum ne adijcias loqui.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d82102-d1e198"> 
          <ref>/ 32.
        <lb ed="#V" n="71"/>c.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d82102-Qd1e200">Loquere maior natum decet enim te. Ado
        <lb ed="#V" n="72" break="no"/>lescens loquere in tua causa vix. Ubi sunt
        <lb ed="#V" n="73"/>senes non multum loquaris.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d82102-d1e211"> 
          <ref>/ 37. c.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d82102-Qd1e213">Hono
        <lb ed="#V" n="74"/>ra medicum propter necessitatem.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d82102-d1e219">
               <lb ed="#V" n="75"/>
       <ref>¶ Tullius retho. artis vereris: li. 2. c. 9.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d82102-Qd1e223">Ob
        <lb ed="#V" n="76" break="no"/>seruantia est per quam homines aliqua digni
        <lb ed="#V" n="77" break="no"/>tate antecedentes cultum: quodam et honore
        <lb ed="#V" n="78"/>dignantur.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d82102-d1e233">
               <lb ed="#V" n="79"/>
          <ref>¶ Petrus apostolus epistola:</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d82102-Qd1e237">Omnes ho
        <lb ed="#V" n="80" break="no"/>norate. Regem honorificate.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d82102-d1e243">
               <lb ed="#V" n="81"/>
          <ref>¶ Paulus apostolus: epistola. i. ad timothe
        <lb ed="#V" n="82"/>um. c. 5.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d82102-Qd1e247">Seniorem ne increpaueris: sed ob
        <lb ed="#V" n="83" break="no"/>secra vt patrem.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d82102-d1e255">
               <lb ed="#V" n="84"/>
         <ref>¶ Lex dig. ti. de obsequiis a liberis et liber
        <lb ed="#V" n="85" break="no"/>tis etc. l. antepenult:</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d82102-Qd1e259">Liberto et filio semper
        <lb ed="#V" n="86"/>honesta et sancta persona patris ac patroni
        <lb ed="#V" n="87"/>videri debet.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d82102-d1e269"> 
          <ref>/ Ti. de iure immunitatis. l. sem
        <lb ed="#V" n="88"/>per. in prin.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d82102-Qd1e271">Iabolenus iurisconsultus ciuis
        <lb ed="#V" n="89"/>romanus ait semper in ciuitate nostra sene
        <lb ed="#V" n="90"/>ctus venerabilis fuit: nam que maiores no <!--245.xml-->
        <pb ed="#V" n="103-v"/>
                  <cb ed="#V" n="a"/>
                  <lb ed="#V" n="1"/>stri pene eundem honorem senibus quam ma
        <lb ed="#V" n="2" break="no"/>gistrantibus tribuebant. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d82102-d1e293">
               <lb ed="#V" n="3"/>
          <ref>¶ Ualerius maximus: lib. 2 ti. de institutis
        <lb ed="#V" n="4"/>antiquis:</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d82102-Qd1e297">Senatui iuuentus ita cumulatum
        <lb ed="#V" n="5"/>et circunspectum honorem reddebat tanquam ma
        <lb ed="#V" n="6"/>iores natum adolescentium communes patres
        <lb ed="#V" n="7"/>essent. Quo circa inuuenes ea die qua consi
        <lb ed="#V" n="8" break="no"/>uium celebrabat senatus conueniebant: vt
        <lb ed="#V" n="9"/>aliquem ex patribus conscriptis: aut pro
        <lb ed="#V" n="10" break="no"/>pinquum: aut paternum amicum ad curiam re
        <lb ed="#V" n="11" break="no"/>ducerent: affixique valuis expectabant do
        <lb ed="#V" n="12" break="no"/>nec reducendi etiam officio fungerentur. Qua
        <lb ed="#V" n="13"/>quidem voluntaria statione et corpora et ani
        <lb ed="#V" n="14" break="no"/>mos ad publica officia impigre substinenda
        <lb ed="#V" n="15"/>roborabant: breuique processu morarum in
        <lb ed="#V" n="16"/>luce virtutum suarum verecunda laboris me
        <lb ed="#V" n="17"/>ditatione ipsi doctores erant.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d82102-d1e331">
               <lb ed="#V" n="18"/>
       <ref>¶ Boetius de consolatione: lib. 3 c. 7.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d82102-Qd1e335">Non
        <lb ed="#V" n="19"/>possumus ob honores reuerentia dignos iu
        <lb ed="#V" n="20" break="no"/>dicare quos ipsis honoribus iudicamus in
        <lb ed="#V" n="21"/>dignos.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d82102-d1e345">
               <lb ed="#V" n="22"/>
          <ref>¶ Isydorus in synonima solliloquiorum: li.
        <lb ed="#V" n="23"/>et.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d82102-Qd1e349">Superiori equalem te non exhibeas.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d82102-d1e355">
               <lb ed="#V" n="24"/>
       <ref>¶ Auctor vel qui dicitur facetus. c. 4.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d82102-Qd1e359">Inter
        <lb ed="#V" n="25"/>maiores caueat ne multa loquatur.</quote>
            </p>
         </div>
